.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d690118543890ba3c806f2d30856ae1212463b08","tid":1526892,"uid":169721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"40d311f2b6bce5d940ae03ac12c522e892cda07b","tid":1526892,"uid":13936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T07:55:00.000Z","msg":"屌你啦<br />\n你地攪左成個月叫人入機場<br />\n呢家又叫人走?<br />\n當初入機場你唔係預班狗唔會過黎呀?<br />\n係咪又想上演上次散水撚事件呀"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T08:31:40.000Z","msg":"咪鼓勵人送頭"},{"pid":"5cdbd39873a9d61f6183e13bc91881b91e346b3a","tid":1526892,"uid":50196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T08:32:24.000Z","msg":"巴打喺現場？"},{"pid":"955d0783935f6b7030fcc32b48d5a5f4fc4bd514","tid":1526892,"uid":35265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T08:33:51.000Z","msg":"唔想走架，但喺現場，你知道出市區嘅交通封晒<br />\n巴士的士塞車入唔到 得返機鐵<br />\n留唔係問題 但要諗定有咩事點走"},{"pid":"d9c978db1c70dc7c3970c762b9cd62d5c8e0aedb","tid":1526892,"uid":257190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T08:34:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8513f92caf77db2bd832d3e2f32516cb8d3e26f1","tid":1526892,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T08:39:26.000Z","msg":"我有個建議 其實圍依D野 有人做左膠方法就得<br />\n個個坐係條路到 成萬人就塞爆所有入口 機場咁外國人睇住應該唔敢清場<br />\n咩野都唔做 其實警犬都做唔到咩<br />\n<br />\n之後再搵人無限來回狗鐵快線 塞爆所有快線就得<br />\n來回快線唔犯法點玩都得<br />\n<br />\n唔好set roadblock 一SET ROAD BLOCK D狗又可以清場<br />\n不過我都係講下 要前線做左膠野 佢地應該唔肯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8764c6fb78585e80142a25197694ca0e2592ab82","tid":1526892,"uid":279927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T08:40:03.000Z","msg":"Be water 留得青山在 不怕沒柴燒"},{"pid":"e01a533c8d9d65508483a603a603168e69f8b2e3","tid":1526892,"uid":168522,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T08:41:57.000Z","msg":"今次popo重裝<br />\n自己人又唔夠多<br />\n留係度等比人拉？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"199580d3c1a8c09be3d47a4d1a817ddbec4a6d2c","tid":1526892,"uid":264556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T08:42:05.000Z","msg":"唔好再靠嚇，唔好再叫人散水，唔好亂發未fact check訊息。大家仲未吸取之前教訓？現場手足會自己衡量風險。而風險大極都唔會大得過市區。<br />\n<br />\n當然要小心，跟大隊，唔落單。上次旅客都要夜晚先走到，今次一定都走唔到，有旅客狗唔會亂黎。<br />\n<br />\n記住機場係春袋，會有大量風向撚千方百計叫你走。但一日未cancel曬啲flight都未算成功。<br />\n<br />\n大家幫手不斷repost message"},{"pid":"59063b89b700baf791a2f0d67d141a60a07b9d3f","tid":1526892,"uid":36421,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8d72528a96dfce12975c5f97a7b15dc63d7a217c","tid":1526892,"uid":232594,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"502c72baeb7bf82549eef4d49f249a9b3c3bc824","tid":1526892,"uid":13936,"like":11,"dislike":18,"score":-7,"quote":{"pid":"f736735b304acc512929695f024b487ae6806ab9","tid":1526892,"uid":16326,"like":32,"dislike":3,"score":29,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T07:58:01.000Z","msg":"咁你比幾百個防暴包圍 你係咪唔走先？<br />\n上次係未有狗黎 就叫散水<br />\n今次見到有狗 唔走特被捕呀？"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T07:59:36.000Z","msg":"咪撚攪抗爭啦<br />\n之前又屌鳩社區抗爭  叫人取消哂入機場<br />\n呢家個個入哂機場又叫人走?<br />\n<br />\n你講丫 有邊次抗爭係無狗呀?<br />\n有狗就走呀? 咁唔撚洗抗爭啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T08:31:25.000Z","msg":"屌你老母留守撚<br />\n留留留，淨係識叫人留，留低就識得抗爭？出tg點避，開槍點避，衝前突襲點避，臥底捉人點避呀？係咪有晒應對方法？？冇就唔該收皮，咁多問題都未解決，淨係叫留，留你老母呀<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>定還是你就係警察臥底叫人留個啲呀</strong></span></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T08:42:40.000Z","msg":"留低又唔一定要開打，和理非散步唔得既。 次次一有狗就話散水。下次吹風入機場一樣會有狗佈防跟住又散水 loops多幾次唔知仲有幾多人會去呢，早幾日仲講到又春袋又盛。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"260a50354e1370670dc43545541f0bd1dc56649f","tid":1526892,"uid":50056,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T08:43:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60342d02cc86ab1d3579506ac1164c9640e08891","tid":1526892,"uid":167753,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T08:43:51.000Z","msg":"今日唔係塞交通咩。佔領機場做乜。。。。"},{"pid":"16c6727f6fbe57080faaefeb3e0cd0bb80d494b2","tid":1526892,"uid":78857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T08:44:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2748ea901a492792cb9fe4205c3e2c007275d570","tid":1526892,"uid":167753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"abaf8ee92ff75cc47cef7700b9e5a5b52cc28ab0","tid":1526892,"uid":100046,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T08:15:18.000Z","msg":"大家要記住 你只係搭車/揸車進行每周末嘅機場交通壓力測試 諗目的先決定應該做啲咩<br />\n<br />\n唔駛慌嘅 揸車同搭車姐 <br />\n驚被圍困？點出入機場？傻啦，旅客搭咩出入 你咪搭咩出入 驚乜野？睇實旅客人數就得啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T08:44:50.000Z","msg":"推呢個"},{"pid":"e0c6081f4e5ef1a16f17f1bc4f362e1ce7c5f157","tid":1526892,"uid":252325,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T08:45:08.000Z","msg":"我都明,知道你由12點坐到依家係好燥底嘅阿SIR"},{"pid":"fc70b04eeecdff3b8ffc8341c8c270ac1be10439","tid":1526892,"uid":188828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T08:46:18.000Z","msg":"今次情況有啲唔同<br />\n因為機鐵運晒遊客走佬<br />\n所以地面得自己友"},{"pid":"481059a76940c44e85ff651c49d13d4ef5fbb398","tid":1526892,"uid":133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T08:47:19.000Z","msg":"走佢老母啦走"},{"pid":"c00a83ce3c1fb9b7d1da3d6264544135168ed71e","tid":1526892,"uid":38472,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T08:47:36.000Z","msg":"上次證明左冇嘢，今次仲走？"},{"pid":"aa554818b45a5f8abb2d61c8c10b83dd7015e645","tid":1526892,"uid":101691,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"502c72baeb7bf82549eef4d49f249a9b3c3bc824","tid":1526892,"uid":13936,"like":11,"dislike":18,"score":-7,"quote":{"p